{"tid":2308680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人類能幫鮭魚洄游？「鮭魚大砲」掀起網路話題","createTime":"2020-12-02T05:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T07:10:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"23281cee1b049d73dbf065bde95757f5b496f377","tid":2308680,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"近日社群媒體流傳一段「鮭魚大砲」（Salmon Cannon）的影片，只見洄游的鮭魚被工作<br />\n人員從河流送進一段懸空的半透明管道，接著就像坐雲霄飛車般，直接越過水壩及其他險<br />\n峻水道回到上游，引發網路熱議。<br />\n <br />\n「鮭魚大砲」是Whooshh Innovations公司的產品，利用魚前後部的差壓推動前進，管道<br />\n也注滿空氣與水霧，讓鮭魚快速輸送時也能呼吸，將一般要費時好幾天的洄游過程，縮短<br />\n到只要幾秒鐘。第一套產品在2014年推出，近日隨著網媒《Cheddar》的介紹影片，在社<br />\n群媒體聲名大噪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.udn.com/news/1126606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.udn.com%2Fnews%2F1126606&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b7be42ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.udn.com/news/1126606</a>"},{"pid":"27ab2200b5989cc68723789eeedebbd247adbcf1","tid":2308680,"uid":136958,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣都算係打亂咗生態平衡 有啲動物都係喺佢哋回游既時候食呢啲魚 依家變保送 咁嗰啲動物食乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec3987b34692c1e77a3879ebd55f9ae03137a02","tid":2308680,"uid":5205,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"D三文魚 會唔會第日唔識游上去游"},{"pid":"60a2fb299c82a2c42f7052596169f652b6b59b0e","tid":2308680,"uid":44454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6ec3987b34692c1e77a3879ebd55f9ae03137a02","tid":2308680,"uid":5205,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"D三文魚 會唔會第日唔識游上去游"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"會， 而家連廢物三文魚都可以有下一代"},{"pid":"ded5d14bdf09081d2f730e8195fd3b3f2ce3ff67","tid":2308680,"uid":311831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27ab2200b5989cc68723789eeedebbd247adbcf1","tid":2308680,"uid":136958,"like":11,"dislike":8,"scor